{"tid":903946,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【體壇性侵】敬佩呂麗瑤勇氣 林鄭：為勇敢行為鼓掌","createTime":"2018-11-16T03:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T12:34:11.000Z","uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7d71bd13559542d9feafb2633f24482421e2575a","tid":903946,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"本港女子跨欄代表呂麗瑤在個人社交網頁，報稱10年前受當時教練性侵犯。特首林鄭月娥在一個活動後表示，對事件感到難過，執法機構會嚴肅跟進，並已聯絡警務處處長積極跟進事件。她對呂公開事件的勇氣感到敬佩，形容對方做法勇敢，要為呂的勇敢行為鼓掌。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥強調，特區政府會竭盡所能保護香港市民，呼籲曾受性侵犯經歷人士，儘管經歷難過，亦要有勇氣作舉報，向執法機構提供資料，或向社會福利署熱線求助。<br />\n<br />\n她指，社會需時常警覺和關心兒童，批評若該職業有較多機會接觸兒童，得到兒童尊敬和信任，何以能作出如此令人憤怒的行為。"},{"pid":"603f13b0acfdf516954ed41b68ec63c789d7a1a6","tid":903946,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5925fc44f64ac5d70112f1f55ce4bff2857de9","tid":903946,"uid":22736,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"依家無罪釋放喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78782b431236bd60bb5e4991b4a013d67cbf8046","tid":903946,"uid":148724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:07:02.000Z","msg":"炒哂車"},{"pid":"ed9c8565e949950ae266069d7d3b38ce9e54d05d","tid":903946,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:12:05.000Z","msg":"19今晚講唔講呢單嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d58174e77b7e6be7f45da4a84cdac9058ac244","tid":903946,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"竹"},{"pid":"896ebc607f5e8e6858474fe8b338d7c5eb6eaf66","tid":903946,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"講到件事係有發生過   只係現今法律告佢唔入咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\